{"title":"云效 CI&CD 实战：代码提交自动构建与部署","date":"2026-07-09T07:47:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2026年7月9日","L":"2026/07/09","MM-DD":"07-09"},"link":"2026/07/09/云效-CI-CD-实战：代码提交自动构建与部署","comments":true,"updated":"2026-07-08T23:48:02.947Z","content":"<p>云效 CI/CD 最常见链路：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Git 推送代码</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">云效 Flow 自动触发</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">拉代码</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">Maven 构建 / 单元测试</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">Docker 镜像构建</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">推送镜像仓库</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">部署到 ECS / Docker / K8s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"一、先建流水线\">一、先建流水线<a title=\"#一、先建流水线\" href=\"#一、先建流水线\"></a></h2>\n<p>进入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">云效 → Flow 流水线 → 新建流水线</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>选择模板可以用：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Java 构建部署</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>或者直接空白流水线。</p>\n<h2 id=\"二、配置代码源触发\">二、配置代码源触发<a title=\"#二、配置代码源触发\" href=\"#二、配置代码源触发\"></a></h2>\n<p>在流水线左侧添加：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">流水线源 / 代码源</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>选择你的仓库，比如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Codeup / GitHub / Gitee / GitLab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后开启：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">代码源触发</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>配置触发分支，例如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">master</span><br><span class=\"line\">dev</span><br><span class=\"line\">test</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>官方文档说明：开启代码源触发并配置 Webhook 后，对应代码地址和分支有提交就可以触发流水线运行。(<a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/zh/yunxiao/user-guide/code-source-trigger?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" title=\"代码源触发-云效(Alibaba Cloud DevOps) - 阿里云文档\" target=\"_blank\">Aliyun Help Center</a>)</p>\n<p>不要优先用顶部那个“通用 Webhook”做代码提交触发。代码仓库触发更适合 push、tag、合并请求这些场景；通用 Webhook 更适合外部系统主动调用流水线。(<a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/zh/yunxiao/user-guide/webhook-trigger-pipeline-1?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" title=\"Webhook 触发流水线 - 阿里云文档\" target=\"_blank\">Aliyun Help Center</a>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"三、maven-构建阶段\">三、Maven 构建阶段<a title=\"#三、maven-构建阶段\" href=\"#三、maven-构建阶段\"></a></h2>\n<p>添加任务：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Java 构建 / Maven 构建</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>命令一般写：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mvn -B clean package -DskipTests</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果要跑测试：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mvn -B clean <span class=\"built_in\">test</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果是多模块项目：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mvn -B clean package -pl assess-server -am -DskipTests</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"四、docker-镜像构建\">四、Docker 镜像构建<a title=\"#四、docker-镜像构建\" href=\"#四、docker-镜像构建\"></a></h2>\n<p>添加任务：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">镜像构建并推送</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>配置：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Dockerfile 路径：./Dockerfile</span><br><span class=\"line\">镜像仓库：阿里云 ACR / 自建 Harbor</span><br><span class=\"line\">镜像版本：$&#123;DATETIME&#125; 或 $&#123;COMMIT_ID&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>建议镜像 tag：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">项目名/服务名:分支名-提交ID</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>例如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">carloan/assess-server:test-$&#123;COMMIT_ID&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"五、部署阶段\">五、部署阶段<a title=\"#五、部署阶段\" href=\"#五、部署阶段\"></a></h2>\n<p>如果你是普通 ECS + Docker，可以用：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">主机部署 / SSH 执行命令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>示例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull 镜像地址</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker stop assess-server || <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker rm assess-server || <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">docker run -d \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --name assess-server \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  -p 8080:8080 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --restart=always \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  镜像地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果你是 Docker Swarm：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker service update \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --image 镜像地址 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  assess-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果是 Kubernetes：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">kubectl <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> image deployment/assess-server assess-server=镜像地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"六、你现在最该这样配\">六、你现在最该这样配<a title=\"#六、你现在最该这样配\" href=\"#六、你现在最该这样配\"></a></h2>\n<p>按你的场景，推荐：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">代码源触发</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">Maven 构建</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">Docker 镜像构建并推送</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ↓</span><br><span class=\"line\">SSH 到服务器执行 docker service update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>核心配置重点是：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight text\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">不是先配 Webhook</span><br><span class=\"line\">而是先在云效流水线源里绑定代码仓库，并开启代码源触发</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>通用 Webhook 只有在你想让“外部系统主动调用云效流水线”时才用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"references\">References<a title=\"#references\" href=\"#references\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://help.aliyun.com/zh/yunxiao/user-guide/code-source-trigger?spm=a2c4g.11186623.0.0.1a462b4aZQjjyR#1cd594bef7hep\" target=\"_blank\">代码源触发-云效(Alibaba Cloud DevOps)-阿里云帮助中心</a></li>\n</ul>\n","next":{"title":"Ubuntu-开发环境配置","link":"2026/07/09/Ubuntu-开发环境配置"},"plink":"https://blog.liumulin.top/2026/07/09/云效-CI-CD-实战：代码提交自动构建与部署/","toc":[{"id":"一、先建流水线","title":"一、先建流水线","index":"1"},{"id":"二、配置代码源触发","title":"二、配置代码源触发","index":"2"},{"id":"三、maven-构建阶段","title":"三、Maven 构建阶段","index":"3"},{"id":"四、docker-镜像构建","title":"四、Docker 镜像构建","index":"4"},{"id":"五、部署阶段","title":"五、部署阶段","index":"5"},{"id":"六、你现在最该这样配","title":"六、你现在最该这样配","index":"6"},{"id":"references","title":"References","index":"7"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"custom":"不许转载😡！！！"}}